data.description: Welcome to Meadow Lane, a breathtaking custom built log home with picturesque views nestled on over 5 acres with custom features throughout the home, where luxury awaits you. From rocking on the oversized front porch, to lounging by the pool, this property provides beautiful woodwork with specialty details throughout. The enormous wrap around porch and extended back porch area exceeds over 2500SF surrounded by nature views. The fieldstone rock wood burning fireplace is the centerpiece of the home. The primary BR complete with sitting area, dressing area, double walk in closets, leading to the ensuite bath provides a quiet oasis. The gourmet kitchen includes a kitchen island, eat at bar, & stainless steel appliances. The home includes multiple spaces that can serve as work space, entertaining or workout spaces. The garage has a wired workshop and bays for parking. Less than 5 minutes from I-85, this retreat is a must see! Previous inspection available for pre-approved buyers.
